<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 space-y-12">

  <!-- Page Heading -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-white">Privacy Policy for <%= client.user.username %></h1>
    <p class="text-white/70"><%= date %></p>
  </div>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Card -->
  <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-6">
    <p class="text-white/70">Thank you for using <%= client.user.username %> (the "Bot"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you interact with the Bot on platforms like Discord. By using the Bot, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>User and Guild Data:</strong> We may collect Discord user ID, username, and guild ID to personalize experiences and manage access.</li>
        <li><strong>Interaction Data:</strong> Commands, messages, and other interactions are logged to ensure functionality.</li>
        <li><strong>Blacklist Data:</strong> If a user or guild is blacklisted, we store the ID and reason solely for moderation purposes.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP addresses, device info, and usage logs may be collected for performance monitoring and abuse prevention.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li>Operate and maintain the Bot, processing commands and responses.</li>
        <li>Moderate and enforce rules, including blacklists.</li>
        <li>Improve features, troubleshoot issues, and analyze usage patterns.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations or protect against fraud, abuse, or security threats.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-white/70">We do not use your data for marketing or sell it to third parties.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Storage:</strong> All data is securely stored in MongoDB. Blacklist data may be retained indefinitely for moderation.</li>
        <li><strong>Security Measures:</strong> Industry-standard practices like encryption and access control are applied. No method of internet transmission is 100% secure.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li>With your explicit consent.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal requests.</li>
        <li>To prevent harm, fraud, or illegal activity, or to enforce terms of service.</li>
        <li>During mergers, acquisitions, or asset sales.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Access and Correction:</strong> Request access or correction of your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion, except for necessary blacklist records.</li>
        <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Stop interacting with the Bot (may limit functionality).</li>
        <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> Request data in a portable format.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-white/70">Contact us to exercise these rights. Discord's policies also apply to data shared on their platform.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70">The Bot is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">7. International Data Transfers</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70">If located outside the U.S., your data may be transferred to and processed in New York City with appropriate safeguards.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70">We may update this policy periodically. Continued use after updates constitutes acceptance.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/70 space-y-1">
        <li>Email: [Your Email Address]</li>
        <li>Discord: [Your Discord Server or Support Channel]</li>
        <li>Website: [Your Website]</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-white/70">By using <%= client.user.username %>, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.</p>
    </section>

    <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-6">Last updated: <%= date %></p>
  </div>

</div>
